scene.message:
Nanjo: Archery's interesting{nl}
too, I suppose... but don't{nl}
forget the hospital.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: They say this club room{nl}
has tons of bows. Maybe I'll{nl}
borrow one and mess around{nl}
sometime.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I'm just no good{nl}
with bows. A razor's more{nl}
my kind of weapon, I guess.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Archery's a refined,{nl}
grown-up sport! Even if you{nl}
don't have a bow, I'll lend{nl}
you one, so it's fine!{waitkey}{ret}
